base_value: Use this app on a daily basis to keep track of the foods and advice I recommend for optimal health and longevity in my books How Not to Die and How Not to Diet.

base_value: The following open source libraries are used: RealmSwift, Charts, FSCalendar, SimpleAnimation and ActiveLabel.

base_value: Set to always be one unit type or enable the 'Units:' toggle button.

base_value: For health alone, use "Daily Dozen Only". For health and weight loss use "Daily Dozen + 21 Tweaks".
